This is a third-party, unofficial toolkit built against the publicly
documented bow.fun contract interfaces (https://bow.fun/docs.html). It is not
affiliated with, endorsed by, or maintained by bow.fun. No warranty is made
about the correctness of the reconstructed interfaces or scripts — always
verify against the live contracts and official docs before using real funds.
